<td valign="top" class="postbody">
<hr />
Got places of interest in the Nasty 'Nati that you've been to or would like to go to or just heard might be haunted? Post them here please!
<br />

<br />
I was contacted by a lady that wanted to learn more about ghost hunting and we're going to meet up at a place that I've always wanted to check out and we're going to hang out and I'm going to answer her questions while we hunt this area.
<br />

<br />
It's a gazeebo (sp?) at Mirror Lake in Eden Park. Apparently there's the ghost of a woman there from the late 1800's to early 1900's or some far off time, whenever it could be. Apparently her husband killed her there or something like that. Reports come from early morning joggers who jog passed this gazeebo and see her standing there waiting for her husband to arrive.
<br />

<br />
I've been to this place twice and both times I've felt an eerie presence there, and this was before I heard about it being haunted. So who knows. But I'll get back to you on this one. It could be this week that I go.</td>
</tr>
